title: Mayors Stimulus-Street Projects 2009
name: Mayors Stimulus-Street Projects 2009
description: This data represents all of the street projects proposed in the Mayors Stimulus Report for 2009. I used a pivot table to get a count of total projects per city along with the sum of funding required and jobs created from those projects. The cities and states were geocoded for latitude and longitude and then uploaded into Geocommons as a csv.
